<br>
The debate within Christianity on whether homosexuality is a sin, etc. will rage on and regardless of what the government does, I think the situation within Christianity will be the same as it is now...some churches/ministers will do them and some won't. Either way, whether Tim and Mike are married/have a civil union whatever, in no way changes my marriage or makes it any less religiously significant to me, so I am not losing sleep over it.<br>
